# Backend code style

**Context:** [`docs/backend-reference.md`](../docs/backend-reference.md) · **Design:** [`design-principles.mdc`](design-principles.mdc) · **Layers:** [`backend-architecture-flow.mdc`](backend-architecture-flow.mdc), [`addon-layering.mdc`](addon-layering.mdc)

## Naming

- File stems under **`src/`**: **camelCase** (`addonMeta.handler.ts`, `xtreamCatalogSync.factory.ts`)
- Functions: verb + domain noun — see [`general-naming-conventions.mdc`](general-naming-conventions.mdc), [`function-operation-naming.mdc`](function-operation-naming.mdc)
- Exported factory mappers: **`camelCase`** + **`Factory`** suffix (`directConfigItemFactory`)
- **`services`** exports: **`fetch*`** / **`get*`** for outbound HTTP — not vague **`run*`** / **`do*`** / **`call*`**

## Formatting

- Braces on every `if` / `else` / `for` / `while` body
- Space inside block braces: `{ like this }`
- Do not nest calls several layers deep — use named locals
- Blank line after imports; external packages, then **`@/`** aliases
- Spaces inside object literals: `{ foo: bar }`

## Module suffixes

| Suffix | Contains |
| --- | --- |
| `*.types.ts` | Types only |
| `*.constants.ts` | `export const` / env literals only — no functions |
| `*.utils.ts` | Pure helpers — no `pool.query`, no axios |
| `*.factory.ts` | Pure mappers — no I/O |
| `*.services.ts` | Outbound HTTP; may use `database` / `factories` |
| `*.db.ts` | SQL only — one **`pool.query`** (or **`client.query` in transaction**) per function; **`withPgTransaction`** for multi-step writes |

## Pragmatism

- Match **known** provider/API shapes — no speculative multi-format parsers
- Normalize at the **service** boundary so callers get a stable shape

## Arguments and state

- Do not quietly mutate caller-owned arrays/maps unless the name says so
- Prefer pure builders; accumulate in the orchestrating handler or job

## Lodash

- [`lodash-usage.mdc`](lodash-usage.mdc): per-function imports (`import _trim from "lodash/trim"`), prefer lodash on unknown-shaped values

## Do not

- Import or edit **`src/temp/`**
- Do not add ad-hoc **migration runners** outside `db/migrations/` unless the user explicitly asks
- Put **`axios`** in **`core/`**, **`pool.query`** in **`factories/`**, or **`handlers`** in **`core/`**

## Tooling

- Run **`npm run format`** and **`npm run lint`** before commit
